{"tid":1959200,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【一套作品】你會揀 漫畫 定 動畫 睇？","createTime":"2020-04-05T08:46:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T01:33:33.000Z","uid":61443,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f9f5e9237a9d1166d1c02062ff84e8c0d932a028","tid":1959200,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T08:46:59.000Z","msg":"我通常睇一套作品<br />\n一係揀 漫畫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一係揀 動畫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇咗一種媒體就算  <br />\n<br />\n因為<br />\n漫畫有漫畫優缺<br />\n動畫有動畫優缺<br />\n所以有時我會煩揀睇 漫畫 定 動畫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16acce30f1b085238b335ebf626f5695a66322cb","tid":1959200,"uid":199776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T08:47:17.000Z","msg":"毒撚"},{"pid":"b4ada129f52d1f6be15d8b11c61a3dac6ce6ab6d","tid":1959200,"uid":117534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T08:47:56.000Z","msg":"兩樣都睇曬"},{"pid":"e6e69cd2b4800a46619cdccdb92660b4d6d6f9ca","tid":1959200,"uid":59661,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T12:55:26.000Z","msg":"睇邊個畫得好啲<br />\n好似鬼𣸵咁漫畫垃圾就會睇動畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6aeef525fa2b851e2daaabc27fe7570c9622fac","tid":1959200,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6e69cd2b4800a46619cdccdb92660b4d6d6f9ca","tid":1959200,"uid":59661,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T12:55:26.000Z","msg":"睇邊個畫得好啲<br />\n好似鬼𣸵咁漫畫垃圾就會睇動畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T14:10:47.000Z","msg":"雖然 死神 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過不得不認早期  <br />\n漫畫分鏡堅高質 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以會睇漫畫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過後期 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b6b394cbbc3a2135f4bcb10766c91d0ff29dabf","tid":1959200,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T14:12:38.000Z","msg":"巨人畫功係好差<br />\n不過就係咁樣啲巨人更加恐怖<br />\n同埋漫畫定格<br />\n比巨人食嗰下絕望感爆燈 <br />\n<br />\n所以睇漫畫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d807627196713d3ea7bfe803272e54873df69318","tid":1959200,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T14:25:53.000Z","msg":"我從來只會睇動畫"},{"pid":"b9a6ffe7f6e8e248a2ca20e086a148f11aaec66a","tid":1959200,"uid":311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T14:28:45.000Z","msg":"漫畫for sure<br />\n多數漫畫先係原作 最貼近原作者想表達既野"},{"pid":"9a8bd81f61ad22256f36357477c62d638f887e00","tid":1959200,"uid":87394,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T14:37:12.000Z","msg":"如果係新番或者動畫好正就追動畫"},{"pid":"ed3648614790fb60bd5eef040592a3bf0ec86eac","tid":1959200,"uid":61443,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b9a6ffe7f6e8e248a2ca20e086a148f11aaec66a","tid":1959200,"uid":311,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T14:28:45.000Z","msg":"漫畫for sure<br />\n多數漫畫先係原作 最貼近原作者想表達既野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T14:41:50.000Z","msg":"火影 我睇咗動畫 <br />\n因為佢啲 BGM 真心正到痴根 <br />\n但係我忍咗佢 200集回憶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0a64501c5558a8188aa165c8bde1cd85a7350dc","tid":1959200,"uid":318474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T14:43:59.000Z","msg":"漫畫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇得快啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bade34fc99028fcbbf02d654bee9d8316ec4fb7","tid":1959200,"uid":128089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-0